657  def degree_to_position(self, degree):
658  """!
659  @brief convert actuator degree to position
660  @details position = degree*(4,095/360)
661 
662  @param[in] data: ros Int8 message
663 
664  @note input constraints:
665  @n - none
666  @note output constraints:
667  @n - none
668  @return none
669  """
670  position = int(degree*(4095/360))
671  return position
672 
673  def height_to_degree(self, height):
674  """!
675  @brief convert actuator degree to position
676  @details position = degree*(4,095/360)
677 
678  @param[in] data: ros Int8 message
679 
680  @note input constraints:
681  @n - none
682  @note output constraints:
683  @n - none
684  @return none
685  """
686  # 25.0 : length of cam follower
687  # 25mm is highst height
688  # -25mm is lowest height
689  # height = height-25.0;
690  degree = 180.0 - ((np.arcsin(height/25.0)*180.0)/np.pi+90.0)
691  return degree
692 
693  def volume_to_height(self, volume):
694  """!
695  @brief convert actuator degree to position
696  @details position = degree*(4,095/360)
697 
698  @param[in] data: ros Int8 message
699 
700  @note input constraints:
701  @n - none
702  @note output constraints:
703  @n - none
704  @return none
705  """
706  # 25.0 : length of cam follower
707  # 25mm is highst height
708  # -25mm is lowest height
709  # height = height-25.0;
710  height = (0.1*float(volume))- 25.0
711  return height

713  def volume_to_position(self, volume):
